OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A shot that lightly wounded a man at a 
OL,6, New Year's Eve party has prompted an   
OL,7, angry political response after it      
OL,8, emerged it was fired from a gun owned  
OL,9, by an Italian far-right MP.            
OL,11,FEmanuele Pozzolo, a member of Prime    
OL,12,FMinister Georgia Meloni's Brothers of  
OL,13,FItaly party, admitted bringing the gun 
OL,14,Fbut denied firing the shot.            
OL,16,FA 31-year-old man was treated in       
OL,17,Fhospital for light wounds to his leg.  
OL,19,FThe centre-left opposition leader has  
OL,20,Fcalled on Ms Meloni to take action.    
